{"tid":1981780,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市回暖】淘大花園呎價重上1.8萬 近半年高位","createTime":"2020-04-21T00:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T00:56:58.000Z","uid":267488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8efedc37727f65c8c3a3399099a464cf87fb72c","tid":1981780,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:49:46.000Z","msg":"九龍灣指標上車屋苑淘大花園，呎價重上1.8萬元。利嘉閣鮑允中稱，淘大花園P座低層3室，實用面積322方呎，屬一房間隔，座向東南兼大單邊，享池景，屬罕有優質放盤，剛以583萬元售出，呎價18,106元，創屋苑呎價近半年新高。單位上年4月放盤，連租約原叫價630萬元，直至本月15日租客搬走後，累減47萬元交吉易手。原業主2012年以268萬元買入，8年升值1.2倍。屋苑本月暫錄得14宗成交，平均呎價15,944元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近半年高位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307a24fc2dea6705245a9287d3e67ff58fcf4962","tid":1981780,"uid":132446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:51:38.000Z","msg":"個別成交， 可能高層加豪裝"},{"pid":"22a9520bc62595d4e90f9a080e29045df97a2f0d","tid":1981780,"uid":70194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:52:10.000Z","msg":"豪裝唔計"},{"pid":"162949bd48c38964de7894571b7166f5c459392a","tid":1981780,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22a9520bc62595d4e90f9a080e29045df97a2f0d","tid":1981780,"uid":70194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:52:10.000Z","msg":"豪裝唔計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:54:13.000Z","msg":"向東南靚景唔計，鳳凰層唔計，鐵路上蓋唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75311e03143bfffb962b561c1d62e170ae4ca6ed","tid":1981780,"uid":73592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:56:24.000Z","msg":"一定係左手交右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7152a428fb12ecf343318f396e8beeb3bc6633b","tid":1981780,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score